.SH NAME
drbd_determine_dev_size \- Sets the right device size obeying all constraints
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "enum determine_dev_size" drbd_determine_dev_size
.BI "(struct drbd_device *device "  ","
.BI "enum dds_flags flags "  ","
.BI "struct resize_parms *rs "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "device" 12
DRBD device.
.IP "flags" 12
-- undescribed --
.IP "rs" 12
-- undescribed --
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns 0 on success, negative return values indicate errors.
You should call \fBdrbd_md_sync\fP after calling this function.
